Long term objectives:

* Album cover / song metadata retrieval
* Playlist/collection manager
* Power button for turning off PC
* Loading DBUS configurations from filesystem
* Dependency injection (dynamic resolution of connection/dbus/commandfactory objects
* Incorporate service providers and intents for third-party access (OpenIntents?)
* Connection profile manager (save/load connection config)
* Reduce battery consumption
* Bluetooth support

Future players to support:
1) Totem / KPlayer
2) Kaffeine / MeTV
3) MythTV
4) MPlayer / Xine
